data.title: Minneapolis StarTribune
data.meta_description: Minneapolis StarTribune - a place for remembering loved ones; a space for sharing memories, life stories, milestones, to express condolences, and celebrate life of your loved ones

Carol Geiger

Geiger, Carol L. 91, of Apple Valley, MN, passed away peacefully on August 26. She is survived by her loving husband of 70 years, George "Dick" Geiger. Wayne Loland

Wayne Arlen Loland, 82, died peacefully in his sleep with his wife of 59 years and 9 1/2 months at his side. He is preceded in death by his mom Myrtle Loland.
